018500 PASS.  MOVE "PASS " TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO PASS-COUNTER.           SG1014.2
018600 FAIL.  MOVE "FAIL*" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO ERROR-COUNTER.          SG1014.2
018700 DE-LETE.  MOVE "*****" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO DELETE-CNT.          SG1014.2
