020200     MOVE CCVS-H-1 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 2 TIMES.   SG1014.2
020300     MOVE CCVS-H-2 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 5 TIMES.   SG1014.2
