051200     MOVE     SPACE TO RE-MARK.                                   SG1044.2
051300 HEAD-ROUTINE.                                                    SG1044.2
051400     MOVE CCVS-H-1 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 2 TIMES.   SG1044.2
051500     MOVE CCVS-H-2 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 5 TIMES.   SG1044.2
051600     MOVE CCVS-H-3 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 3 TIMES.   SG1044.2
